Class Person

  • java.lang.Object
    • Person
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Customer

    public abstract class Person
extends java.lang.Object
    The Person abstract class will be used hold all information relating to a person. Since it is an abstract class, this class cannot be instantiated. It will primarily be used for inheriting attributes
    Since:
    9/27/2020
    Version:
